{"tid":1079273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一夜情後付不起500元　男模仿電視劇把女網友捂死","createTime":"2019-03-26T23:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T11:56:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"ca73d7a0e71745aa976f9e3caba4f095fd661daf","tid":1079273,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T23:51:20.000Z","msg":"中國湖南郴州市一名23歲的彭姓男子，日前與陳姓女網友一夜情後，因為付不起500元人民幣（約2295元台幣），憤而把對方殺死，再把屍體塞進行李箱，丟棄於河中。當地中級人民法院近日審理本案，彭男被控故意殺人罪、盜竊罪。<br />\n起訴書指，彭男於去年8月23日下午5時許，約陳女在賓館見面後，2人發生性關係，結束後因為「價錢」談不攏，雙方發生衝突。身無分文的彭男，不滿陳女索價500元人民幣，於是用沾有酒精的毛巾捂住她的口鼻，把她活活悶死。<br />\n當天傍晚6時許，彭男把陳女的屍體用浴巾打包，塞進行李箱，離開賓館後，用陳女的錢，搭乘計程車回郴州棄屍。3天後（8月26日）有工人清理河道時，發現行李箱，才讓命案曝光。<br />\n彭男在法庭上辯稱，他本來爽完，想直接離開，沒想到陳女早一步扣住他的身分證，要求支付500元的報酬，「我告訴她我沒有錢，但是她還是要求我付錢」。他本來想找朋友送錢過來，但進到洗手間後，看到一小瓶酒精，決定模仿電視劇把陳女弄昏，「電視劇裡有人用酒精可以把人捂暈，我想把陳女捂暈後，拿走自己的身份證離開」。<br />\n彭男續稱，後來他趁陳女在床上玩手機時，用沾有酒精的毛巾捂住她的口鼻，「捂了大概3分鐘，直到陳女沒有反抗才將毛巾拿開」。但萬萬沒想到，陳女不但暈了過去，還沒了呼吸，他急忙為對方心肺復甦，眼見回天乏術，只好把陳女塞進行李箱，順便把她身上的700元（約3214元台幣）現金、兩張銀行卡，及支付寶帳號內的6000多元（約2.75萬元台幣）的財物據為己有。<br />\n彭男也向法官求情，因為不景氣，他失業後經濟狀況不是很好，不但一直住在朋友家，也只能靠向家裡要錢過活。法官聽完後，未當庭宣判。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_f57f8d2ae646a53d3e37110395c7e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_f57f8d2ae646a53d3e37110395c7e5d2.jpg&h=01e43706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_7cf9014096f7ff611cc7ab06a8388aac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_7cf9014096f7ff611cc7ab06a8388aac.jpg&h=94e66ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_93f3d5db9cafb12db94096b011fcf9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_93f3d5db9cafb12db94096b011fcf9e8.jpg&h=321deec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190327/1540428/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190327%2F1540428%2F&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=d098c7ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190327%2F1540428%2F&h=76a026bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190327/1540428/</a>"},{"pid":"ad08eebb8c62f5db82a45613d1b2d61742d88ff2","tid":1079273,"uid":192813,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T23:52:31.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"b6eea70a729ada1a0cfa347347f9ec8b01354e56","tid":1079273,"uid":169662,"like":297,"dislike":2,"score":295,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T23:57:06.000Z","msg":"一夜情要收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雞"},{"pid":"ed526c102ce2f72784ff7063422bd9c721a5521b","tid":1079273,"uid":6222,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"下 ons都要收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2017492d04ed85ca20957635581b5bffbb581ae7","tid":1079273,"uid":33497,"like":357,"dislike":1,"score":356,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:09:24.000Z","msg":"23歲咁撚樣？"},{"pid":"9bfaf95a946f1a540fa25f211098c84cba45eda7","tid":1079273,"uid":108418,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"強姦係台灣，殺人係終幗"},{"pid":"b1399bc8dd0d1d26cf2fceea2ee52135631ef1ec","tid":1079273,"uid":49853,"like":158,"dislike":1,"score":157,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:10:49.000Z","msg":"23歲成53歲咁"},{"pid":"af0016bca060a2e18b4b78268d3238ae933d20e0","tid":1079273,"uid":204571,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2017492d04ed85ca20957635581b5bffbb581ae7","tid":1079273,"uid":33497,"like":357,"dislike":1,"score":356,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:09:2