00Z","msg":"點解可以拎到條女支付寶入面d錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db52b18aa88b96512dbbcfe7c6a17ec012aa674","tid":1079273,"uid":759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"要比錢都算一夜情咩"},{"pid":"cf387c358fda79746398eef4df28a07f0e7f555e","tid":1079273,"uid":199820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國湖南郴州市一名23歲的彭姓男子，日前與陳姓女網友一夜情後，因為付不起500元人民幣（約2295元台幣），憤而把對方殺死，再把屍體塞進行李箱，丟棄於河中。當地中級人民法院近日審理本案，彭男被控故意殺人罪、盜竊罪。<br />\n起訴書指，彭男於去年8月23日下午5時許，約陳女在賓館見面後，2人發生性關係，結束後因為「價錢」談不攏，雙方發生衝突。身無分文的彭男，不滿陳女索價500元人民幣，於是用沾有酒精的毛巾捂住她的口鼻，把她活活悶死。<br />\n當天傍晚6時許，彭男把陳女的屍體用浴巾打包，塞進行李箱，離開賓館後，用陳女的錢，搭乘計程車回郴州棄屍。3天後（8月26日）有工人清理河道時，發現行李箱，才讓命案曝光。<br />\n彭男在法庭上辯稱，他本來爽完，想直接離開，沒想到陳女早一步扣住他的身分證，要求支付500元的報酬，「我告訴她我沒有錢，但是她還是要求我付錢」。他本來想找朋友送錢過來，但進到洗手間後，<span style=\"color: red;\">看到一小瓶酒精，決定模仿電視劇把陳女弄昏，「電視劇裡有人用酒精可以把人捂暈</span>，我想把陳女捂暈後，拿走自己的身份證離開」。<br />\n彭男續稱，後來他趁陳女在床上玩手機時，用沾有酒精的毛巾捂住她的口鼻，「捂了大概3分鐘，直到陳女沒有反抗才將毛巾拿開」。但萬萬沒想到，陳女不但暈了過去，還沒了呼吸，他急忙為對方心肺復甦，眼見回天乏術，只好把陳女塞進行李箱，順便把她身上的700元（約3214元台幣）現金、兩張銀行卡，及支付寶帳號內的6000多元（約2.75萬元台幣）的財物據為己有。<br />\n彭男也向法官求情，因為不景氣，他失業後經濟狀況不是很好，不但一直住在朋友家，也只能靠向家裡要錢過活。法官聽完後，未當庭宣判。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_f57f8d2ae646a53d3e37110395c7e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_f57f8d2ae646a53d3e37110395c7e5d2.jpg&h=01e43706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_7cf9014096f7ff611cc7ab06a8388aac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_7cf9014096f7ff611cc7ab06a8388aac.jpg&h=94e66ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190327/640_93f3d5db9cafb12db94096b011fcf9e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190327%2F640_93f3d5db9cafb12db94096b011fcf9e8.jpg&h=321deec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190327/1540428/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190327%2F1540428%2F&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5ZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=d098c7ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190327%2F1540428%2F&h=76a026bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190327/1540428/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c3b1b4187dfec76b37d5e68df74f40422aeb97","tid":1079273,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bfaf95a946f1a540fa25f211098c84cba45eda7","tid":1079273,"uid":108418,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"強姦係台灣，殺人係終幗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n風化係台灣，重口味係印度"},{"pid":"5cce634c9ca52081fd93b0b155dc3b84381f989a","tid":1079273,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"食霸王G重殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50df513378646fa04d5f59621ad103ba27a61d4","tid":1079273,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"爭住先啦on9<br />\n嘈完就有錢咩<br />\n依家死埋啦臭雞"},{"pid":"486bc0cbf2ac4cca4823fd92cad1cdf62d9bbc6f","tid":1079273,"uid":123012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b28daf28ecc7